Sparkfun electronics makes a simple IR remote that has nine buttons. It can be purchased at Sparkfun.com

The remote sends 32bit HEX codes and requires a 38khz IR receiver. 

Button       Code

Power        10EFD827
A            10EFF807
B            10EF7887
C            10EF58A7
Up           10EFA05F
Down         10EF807F
Left         10EF10EF
Right        10EF807F
Circle       10EF20DF
